sentence: show me one way flights from indianapolis to memphis before ten a m on any day
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_days||'"', '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 v0.departure_time, '"'||v5.flight_id||'"', '"'||v6.fare_id||'"',
 '"'||v6.round_trip_required||'"' FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1, city v2, airport_service v3, city v4,
 flight_fare v5, fare v6 
WHERE ((v0.flight_days = 'DAILY') 
AND (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'INDIANAPOLIS'))) 
AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'MEMPHIS'))) 
AND ((v0.departure_time <  1000) AND ((v0.flight_id = ANY v5.flight_id) 
AND ((v5.fare_id = ANY v6.fare_id) AND ((v6.round_trip_required = 'NO') 
AND ( 1 =  1))))))));
